[Outro]
親父、元気か？ 俺たちは元気だ
最後に報告が、俺は揺るがないものを手にした
それは、家族だ だから、頼むな
俺が死んだら約束通り ２人で酒呑もうな

ROMAJI

Oyaji, genki ka? kocchi wa ii tenki da
Ima, chotto shabette heiki ka?
Ma, jikan ga nē wake ja nē shi na
Are kara 20 nen konna n iu no mo jibun de
Otonage nee no mo wakatte kkedo
Ore wa anta o nikunderu
Itta yo na? 21 nen mae no ano yoru
Ie ni kāchan wa i nakatta
Dakara, denwa ga nare ba juwaki o toru
E? nan datte? jitsuwa ore ni wa kyōdai ga iru?
Denwa shiro tte donna riyū?
Demo, son ji wa ureshikatta yo jibun
Baka da yo na denwa shichimatta ima omoe ba
Nīchan no sono koe ga meiwaku sō na no ga kotae da
Otoko da kara kotae ta demo buccha keta banashi kotae ta
De, itsumo no tōri anta no renraku wa todae ta


[ Verse 2 : hannya ]
Demo, warui hanashi bakkari ja nai
Ore no kioku da to are wa 10 sai
Tsure te tte kure ta yo ne? sākasu
Raion ga ore tachi o wakasu
Tsugini atta no wa chū 1
Taibu otona ni natta funiki'
Itta anta to iware ta ore wa
Dō utsutta? shibuya no yūhi ni
94 nen 7-gatsu anta no yōdai ga ki ni naru
Mukatta saki kita ku no byōin kango fu no koe ga tōi
3 ka mae? 4 ka mae? semi no koe goccha maze
Kansha shiteru ima shashin no anta o miteru
Katei no koto mo uso tsui ta kokuseki no koto mo uso tsui ta
Demo, temē ga nani mo shira nē tokoro de hitori no onna wa tsuyoku i ta
Demo, anta to i tara dō natta?
Kore dakyaieru te ni wakka
Korosa naku te yokatta
Ai o uke te ore wa sodatta


[ Verse 3 : KOHH ]
Ai o uke te ore mo sodatta
1992 nen 1 tsuki 15 nichi ga papa no meinichi
2 sai no koro no kioku nē shi bideo to shashin dake mi te imēji
Sorede mama wa seishin byōin ni i ta
Ore ga shichi go san no toki 'tatsuo ga watashi o yonderu' tsutte
9 kai beranda kara tobiori te jisatsu shiyo u to suru
Nai te saken de abare te shinu tte iu
Ore wa anta o nikunderu
Papa ga shin da no wa kōtsū jiko tte kikasare ta
Minna sō iu shi sō omotte ta yo ima made wa
Jikka de jīchan to issho ni mazu i tabako o sutte i ta ano toki
'tatsuo wa jikoshi ja nai n da zo' tte
Iware te ji-chan nokoto san do mi
Maji ka yo na n da sore
Shinjitsu o shiru no nanka koee kedo
Kekkyoku u ya muya ni gomakasare ta ore
Mada hontō no koto wa shira nai ore no kanguri ja ōbādōzu
Mayonaka kameido no o haka ni itte issho ni remon chiyuu hai o nomu
Nē kou tatsuo kiiteru ka ore no ongaku o
Nihonjin dakedo kankoku no otōsan no namae ore mo tsukau yo
'KOHH'


